headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get Double Rewards on Special Cargo Sales and More
content:
Don’t just make a living — make a killing. Is your Warehouse overflowing with deadstock and contraband that’s too hot to handle? No better time to offload than right now: all Special Cargo Sell Missions are paying out 2X GTA$ and RP through October 13, so you’ll make a pretty penny.

Use the Ad-Hawk laptop in your Warehouse to choose the amount of cargo you’d like to sell either by land, by sea, or by air. The choice is yours, good luck.
